title: What product should Richie.shop add next?
body:
Richie.shop has been live for about 10 days and sold 3 orders. It currently has 5 products which are manufactured on-demand in regions closest to customers to reduce carbon footprints.  In order to boost sales, more product selection is needed.  
What products would you be interested in on https://richie.shop ?
